
1. Define version number in retrace.spec
2. Rename the directory of source code into retrace-[version]
3. Make tar.gz archive file

        > tar cvzf retrace-[version].tar.gz retrace-[version]

4. Copy archive file into /root/rpmbuild/SOURCES
5. Run rpmbuild command

        > rpmbuild -ba retrace.spec

6. The RPM file will be generated in /root/rpmbuild/RPMS directory
